<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.3">
<l>piḷḷai yuruvāyt tayiruṇ ṭaṭiyēṉ</l>
<l>uḷḷam pukunta voruva rūrpōl</l>
<l>kaḷḷa nārai vayaluḷ kayalmīṉ</l>
<l>koḷḷai koḷḷuṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where sly herons snatch</l>
<l>Kayal fish in the paddy fields [as their] booty,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the one who, having eaten curds</l>
<l>In the form of a child, entered the heart of [this] devotee, me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
